Carrot and Ginger Vinegrette
  --Cook's Country

2 carrots, peeled and chopped
1/4 c seasoned rice vinegar
2 tbsp water
1 1/2" piece ginger, peeled and coarsely chopped
1 tsp toasted sesame oil
1/2 tsp salt
1/4 c vegetable oil

Process everything but oil in blender until finely ground, ~30 s. With blender running, slowly drizzle oil and process until smooth, ~30 s.
